            <title>[LOG4J2-2107] MapMessage should support both StringBuilderFormattable and MultiformatMessage</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-2107</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently MessagePatternConverter will not respect the format, writing the MapMessage directly to a shared StringBuilder using the default encoding.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need to implement a &quot;MultiFormatStringBuilderFormattable&quot; type with &quot;void formatTo(String[] formats, StringBuilder buffer);&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
